---
title: ¡Bienvenido a Historiana!
---

- images = %w[cabin cake circus game safe submarine]

header.masthead.bg-light.text-center
  .container.d-flex.align-items-center.flex-column.flex-md-row
    img.masthead-avatar.mb-5.flex-md-shrink-0 alt="Ana" src="#{image_path('ana.jpg')}" /
    .flex-md-grow-1
      h1.masthead-heading.text-uppercase.mb-0 Historiana
      =partial "divider", locals: { theme: "dark", icon: "fa-feather-alt"  }
      p.masthead-subheading.font-weight-light.mb-0 Apasionada por crear hermosas historias

section#portfolio.page-section.portfolio
  .container
    h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-secondary.mb-0 Portafolio
    =partial "divider", locals: { icon: "fa-briefcase" }
    .row.justify-content-center
      - images.each_with_index do |name, index|
        .col-md-6.col-lg-4.mb-5
          .portfolio-item.mx-auto data-bs-target="#portfolioModal#{index + 1}" data-bs-toggle="modal"
            .portfolio-item-caption.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center.h-100.w-100
              .portfolio-item-caption-content.text-center.text-white
                i.fas.fa-plus.fa-3x
            img.img-fluid alt="#{name}" src="#{image_path("portfolio/#{name}.png")}" /

section#about.page-section.bg-secondary.text-white.mb-0
  .container
    h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-white Acerca de
    =partial "divider", locals: { theme: "light", icon: "fa-user" }
    .row
      .col-lg-4.ms-auto
        p.lead Como estudiante de humanidades de toda la vida, encuentro que la historia, el arte y la literatura son materias que fomentan mi autodesarrollo.
      .col-lg-4.me-auto
        p.lead Mi trabajo ideal es un entorno orientado a las personas donde pueda dedicarme a enseñar, escribir, traducir o corregir textos con la oportunidad de aprender, crecer y contribuir al mundo.
    .text-center.mt-4
      a.btn.btn-xl.btn-outline-light href="#"
        i.fas.fa-download.me-2
        | ¡Descarga mi CV!

section#blog.page-section.bg-light.mb-0
  .container
    h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase Blog
    =partial "divider", locals: { theme: "dark", icon: "fa-pencil-alt" }
    .row
      .col-lg-12
        p.lead Próximamente...

section#contact.page-section
  .container
    h2.page-section-heading.text-center.text-uppercase.text-secondary.mb-0 Contáctame
    =partial "divider", locals: { icon: "fa-paper-plane" }
    .row.justify-content-center
      .col-lg-8.col-xl-7
        form
          .form-floating
            input#inputName.form-control placeholder=("Ingresa tu nombre...") type="text" /
            label for="inputName"  Nombre
          .form-floating
            input#inputEmail.form-control placeholder=("Ingresa tu correo electrónico...") type="email" /
            label for="inputEmail"  Correo electrónico
          .form-floating
            input#inputPhone.form-control placeholder=("Ingresa tu número telefónico...") type="tel" /
            label for="inputPhone"  Número Telefónico
          .form-floating
            textarea#inputMessage.form-control placeholder=("Ingresa el mensaje...") style=("height: 12rem")
            label for="inputMessage"  Mensaje
          br/
          button.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl type="submit"  Enviar

  - %w[Cabaña Pastel Circo Videojuego Seguridad Submarino].each_with_index do |name, index|
    .portfolio-modal.modal.fade aria-hidden="true" aria-labelledby="portfolioModal1" tabindex="-1" id="portfolioModal#{index + 1}"
      .modal-dialog.modal-xl
        .modal-content
          .modal-header.border-0
            button.btn-close aria-label="Close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" type="button"
          .modal-body.text-center.pb-5
            .container
              .row.justify-content-center
                .col-lg-8
                  h2.portfolio-modal-title.text-secondary.text-uppercase.mb-0=name
                  =partial "divider"
                  img.img-fluid.rounded.mb-5 alt="#{images[index]}" src="#{image_path("portfolio/#{images[index]}.png")}" /
                  p.mb-4 Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Mollitia neque assumenda ipsam nihil, molestias magnam, recusandae quos quis inventore quisquam velit asperiores, vitae? Reprehenderit soluta, eos quod consequuntur itaque. Nam.
                  button.btn.btn-primary data-bs-dismiss="modal" href="#!"
                    i.fas.fa-times.fa-fw
                    | Cerrar
